Featuring a full-sized QWERTY layout and scissor-switch keys, this keyboard provides all the essential keys and commands with a responsive and tactile typing experience. Dedicated keys for Cut, Copy, and Paste boost productivity, making tasks like drafting documents or entering data more efficient. With Bluetooth 3.0 connectivity, you can enjoy a wireless, clutter-free workspace, and the ability to sync with up to three devices allows for easy switching between systems. The keyboard includes a USB Type-C cable for recharging, offering up to 80 hours of battery life per charge. Extended Bluetooth Keyboard upgrade your existing Mac keyboard to a sleek wireless keyboard with full numeric keypad, Bluetooth connection and responsive scissor-switch keys  Wireless 3 Devices Sync Connect to 3 Bluetooth devices at a time and use the assigned Bluetooth keys to switch between your smartphone, tablet or laptop  Initutive Shortcut Keys Equipped with convenient shortcut function keys, specifically designed for Mac devices to switch apps, search, screenshot, copy/paste and more USB-C Rechargable Port Features a built-in USB-C rechargeable port for long-lasting battery life up to 80 hours of uninterrupted work time between charges  Device Compatibility This keyboard is compatible with a wide range of Apple devices released after 2012, including the iMac Pro, iMac, 2020/2018 Mac mini, 2020/2019/2018/2017/2016 MacBook Pro, 2020/2018 MacBook Air, MacBook, 2019 iPad, 2020/2018 iPad Pro, iPhone 11 Pro Max/11 Pro/11, XS Max/XS/XR/X, 8 Plus/8, as well as iOS and macOS devices. Requires macOS v10.4 or later. What's in the box?
